entries.femaleVariant: 'Eyyyy, how's life in NC? Gettin' any sleep? 'Cause I'm not! Not when there's money to be made!
So listen, one of my people – name's Juliet – was supposed to deliver me some precious data. Never made it – gettin' total radio silence.
Check on her, will you? And, uh, don't forget the data. Spec's attached.
